        <title>Classroom activity example: Digital literacy and self-management</title>
        <content>&lt;!--REPLACE MAIN IMAGE--&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width="550" height="386" alt=" Workforce preparation skills and competencies graphic, which include Skills: basic academic skills, critical thinking, digital literacy and self-management, and competencies: utilizing resources, using information, working with others, understanding systems, skills necessary for successful transition into and completion of postsecondary education or employment" src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/OG_DigitalLiteracy.jpg" usemap="#navmap" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
